description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to appoint a full time Specialty Doctor to Devon Ward Ward, a 12 bedded male &lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;psychiatric intensive care unit&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;based at Chase Farm Hospital. The ward receives patients living in all three boroughs of the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post has previously been occupied by an agency specialty doctor, who has been employed to provide more senior medical support to the junior staff grade doctor on the ward. We have recently been able to develop the post as a substantive part of the medical establishment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Maria Ivanov, Consultant Psychiatrist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mariaivanov@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;020 8702 4086&lt;/p&gt;
